You are a rolling hedgehog in a forset set ablaze. You must roll your way to the safety tree. Its faster if you roll, ya know?
That would be easy if it weren't for the fire balls surrounding you. Avoid the fire balls and get to safety! Hit the fire balls,
and its all over.

Hedgehog - 
Fire - https://stealthix.itch.io/animated-fires or https://codemanu.itch.io/pixelart-effect-pack
Tree - https://heirey.itch.io/mud-knight
Background - https://ansimuz.itch.io/parallax-forest
Ramp - https://ansimuz.itch.io/sunnyland-forest
